org.jgrapes.core

Class Components.PoolingIndex<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jgrapes.core.Components.PoolingIndex<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the key type
    V - the value type
    Enclosing class:
    Components

    public static class Components.PoolingIndex<K,V>
extends Object

    An index of pooled items. Each key is associated with a set of values. Values can be added or retrieved from the set.
